text: Anny van Doorne (26 February 1930 - 6 April 2004) was a Dutch equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2004 deaths Category:Dutch female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Netherlands Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Eindhoven
